<div type="a">
<column>5</column>
<head>An Improvement Demanded</head>
<origin></origin>
<commentary></commentary>
<transcript></transcript>
<trailer></trailer>
<names></names>
<summary>The editors describe the scene on the road to the Cemetery during a recent funeral.
The road has deteriorated so badly that the cart carrying the coffin was upset and the coffin was
tossed to the ground. The editors declare this a disgrace to the community and demand that the
City Council improve the street quickly.</summary>
<note></note>
<look></look>
</div>

